Name: array
Doc: The Array object represents a list of elements.

Methods.Name: kutalika
Methods.Doc: Returns the number of elements in an array.

Methods.Name: chotsaKumbuyo
Methods.Doc: Removes the last element from an array and returns that element. This method changes the length of the array.

Methods.Name: Kankha
Methods.Doc: Adds one or more elements to the end of an array and returns the new length of the array.

Methods.Name: chotsaKutsogolo
Methods.Doc: Removes the first element from an array and returns that element. This method changes the length of the array.
